e and understand 替代件供应链稳定性；多品牌覆盖；出口包装. Our solutions are specifically designed to address these challenges effectively.\n\n\nWhy partner with us:\n✅ OEM-grade quality at competitive prices\n✅ MOQ as low as 50 sets per model\n\n\n\n\n\n\n✅ Full export support: packaging, documentation, logistics\n✅ Custom branding and packaging available\n✅ Sample support for quality verification\n\n✅ Comprehensive after-sales support including product training and technical assistance\n\n\n\n\nWith your focus on 全球出口（中东、非洲、东南亚、南美）, our products are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\n\nAs a distributor focused on 三菱及日欧品牌全车件：发动机、传动、悬挂、车身、电气, adding our cost-effective exterior parts can significantly boost your margins while maintaining quality standards for your customers.\n\n\n1980年代成立，三菱授权，有专门出口公司，替代件需求大\n\n\nWe\'d love to send you our product catalog and sample pricing. Would you be available for a brief call next week to discuss your specific needs?\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nBest regards,\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\n佛山市鼎和盛汽车配件有限公司\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China\n','Competitive MitsubishiandJapanese and... Supply - Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd | Boost Your Margins','Dear ThailandAutopart.com (Thai Mitsu/Universal/Siam Bliss) Team,\n\nHope this email finds you well! My name is Leo Leung from Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd, a leading Chinese auto parts factory specializing in exterior components for pickup trucks, SUVs, and passenger vehicles.\n\nWith your strong presence in MitsubishiandJapanese and European brandsFull vehicle parts：Engine parts、Transmission、Suspension、Body、Electrical, we believe we can be your ideal supplier for:\n• Mirror、Fog lamp covers、Grilles、Pillar trims、Roof racks\n\n\nWhy partner with us:\n✅ OEM-grade quality at competitive prices\n✅ MOQ as low as 50 sets per model\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n✅ Full export support: packaging, documentation, logistics\n✅ Custom branding and packaging available\n✅ Sample support for quality verification\n\n\n✅ Comprehensive after-sales support including product training and technical assistance\n\n\n\n\nWe\'ve analyzed the supply chain landscape and understand Replacement partsSupply chainStability；Multi-brandcoverage；Export packaging. Our solutions are specifically designed to address these challenges effectively.\n\n\n\nWith your focus on Global export（Middle East、Africa、Southeast Asia、South America）, our products are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\nAs a distributor focused on MitsubishiandJapanese and European brandsFull vehicle parts：Engine parts、Transmission、Suspension、Body、Electrical, adding our cost-effective exterior parts can significantly boost your margins while maintaining quality standards for your customers.\n\n\n\n\nEstablished in 1980sEstablished，MitsubishiAuthorized，with dedicatedExport company，Replacement partsDemandhigh\n\n\nWe\'d love to send you our product catalog and sample pricing. Would you be available for a brief call next week to discuss your specific needs?\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China',91,'A',NULL,1,1,0,NULL,0,'Industry_Directory','泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户开发清单_完整版.xlsx',NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 19:00:26','2026-06-26 20:20:43',NULL,'网站询盘系统',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
