型配件SKU管理. Our solutions are specifically designed to address these challenges effectively.\n\n\nWhy partner with us:\n✅ OEM-grade quality at competitive prices\n✅ MOQ as low as 50 sets per model\n\n\n\n\n\n\n✅ Full export support: packaging, documentation, logistics\n✅ Custom branding and packaging available\n✅ Sample support for quality verification\n\n✅ Comprehensive after-sales support including product training and technical assistance\n\n\n\n\nWith your focus on 泰国、迪拜/中东、非洲、东南亚（全球出口）, our products are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\n\nAs a distributor focused on 丰田Hilux/4x4全车配件：保险杠、翼子板、引擎盖、车门、后视镜、灯具、车身面板, adding our cost-effective exterior parts can significantly boost your margins while maintaining quality standards for your customers.\n\n\n泰国最大4x4出口商，以全球最低价为卖点\n\n\nWe\'d love to send you our product catalog and sample pricing. Would you be available for a brief call next week to discuss your specific needs?\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nBest regards,\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\n佛山市鼎和盛汽车配件有限公司\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China\n','Competitive ToyotaHilux/4x4Full vehicle... Supply - Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd | Boost Your Margins','Dear Jim Autos Thailand (Thailand4x4) Team,\n\nHope this email finds you well! My name is Leo Leung from Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd, a leading Chinese auto parts factory specializing in exterior components for pickup trucks, SUVs, and passenger vehicles.\n\nWith your strong presence in ToyotaHilux/4x4Full vehicle accessories：Bumpers、Fenders、Hoods、Doors、Mirror、Lights/Lamps、Body panels, we believe we can be your ideal supplier for:\n• ToyotaHiluxBumpers、MediumGrilleGrilles、Fog lamp covers、MirrorHousing、Roof racks、Side skirts\n\n\nWhy partner with us:\n✅ OEM-grade quality at competitive prices\n✅ MOQ as low as 50 sets per model\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n✅ Full export support: packaging, documentation, logistics\n✅ Custom branding and packaging available\n✅ Sample support for quality verification\n\n\n✅ Comprehensive after-sales support including product training and technical assistance\n\n\n\n\nWe\'ve analyzed the supply chain landscape and understand need continuousLow-cost suppliers；Multi-modelPartsSKU management. Our solutions are specifically designed to address these challenges effectively.\n\n\n\nWith your focus on Thailand、Dubai/Middle East、Africa、Southeast Asia（Global export）, our products are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\nAs a distributor focused on ToyotaHilux/4x4Full vehicle accessories：Bumpers、Fenders、Hoods、Doors、Mirror、Lights/Lamps、Body panels, adding our cost-effective exterior parts can significantly boost your margins while maintaining quality standards for your customers.\n\n\n\n\nThailandLargest4x4 exporter，known forLowest global prices\n\n\nWe\'d love to send you our product catalog and sample pricing. Would you be available for a brief call next week to discuss your specific needs?\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China',91,'A',NULL,1,1,0,NULL,0,'Industry_Directory','泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户开发清单_完整版.xlsx',NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 19:00:26','2026-06-26 20:21:46',NULL,'网站询盘系统',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
