analyzed the supply chain landscape and understand 出口美国需稳定供货；多车型模具开发成本高. Our solutions are specifically designed to address these challenges effectively.\n\n\nOur OEM Partnership Advantages:\n\n\n\n\n? Custom tooling development in 30-45 days\n? Flexible MOQ: 50 sets per model for trial production\n\n\n\n\n\n\n? Stable batch consistency with full traceability\n\n✅ Comprehensive after-sales support including product training and technical assistance\n\n\n\n\nWith your focus on 泰国、美国、中东、东南亚, our products are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\n\n上市公司，车身件为主营，产品100%匹配\n\n\nWould you be interested in reviewing our product catalog and discussing how we can support your manufacturing operations?\n\nPlease visit our website: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nBest regards,\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\n佛山市鼎和盛汽车配件有限公司\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China\n','OEM Quality Exterior body... Supplier - Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd | Enhance Your Production','Dear Fortune Parts Industry Public Company Limited (FPI) Team,\n\nGreetings from Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd! We are a professional automotive exterior parts manufacturer based in Foshan, China, with over 10 years of experience serving global OEM clients.\n\nWith your expertise in Exterior body parts：Bumpers、Grilles、Fenders、Hoods、内Fenders、Tail lights、high灯、Bodykits、Fog lights, we believe we can be your ideal partner for:\n• MediumGrilleGrilles、Fog lamp covers、Bumpers、Fenders\n\n\nWhy partner with us:\n✅ OEM-grade quality at competitive prices\n✅ MOQ as low as 50 sets per model\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n✅ Full export support: packaging, documentation, logistics\n✅ Custom branding and packaging available\n✅ Sample support for quality verification\n\n\n✅ Comprehensive after-sales support including product training and technical assistance\n\n\n\n\nWe\'ve analyzed the supply chain landscape and understand export美国需稳定Supply；Multi-modelMold developmentCostHigh. Our solutions are specifically designed to address these challenges effectively.\n\n\n\nWith your focus on Thailand、美国、Middle East、Southeast Asia, our products are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\n\n\n\nListed company，Body件为Main business，100% product match\n\n\nWe\'d love to discuss how we can support your OEM production needs. Would you be available for a brief call next week?\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China',90,'A',NULL,1,1,0,NULL,0,'Industry_Directory','泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户开发清单_完整版.xlsx',NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 19:00:26','2026-06-26 20:21:49',NULL,'(MS. NATTIYA KLINCHAN - Export Sales Manager)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
