ng.\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China',70,'B',NULL,1,1,0,NULL,0,'Industry_Directory','泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户开发清单_完整版.xlsx',NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 19:00:26','2026-06-26 20:20:50',NULL,'客户服务热线',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
