s are well-positioned to meet local market demands.\n\n\n\n\n\nSpecializing in密封条和PlasticFenders，有分产品重叠\n\n\nLet us simplify your China sourcing. Would you be interested in receiving our product catalog and competitive pricing?\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China',67,'B',NULL,1,1,0,NULL,0,'Industry_Directory','泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户分析报告.txt; 泰国汽车配件客户开发清单_完整版.xlsx',NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 19:00:27','2026-06-26 20:21:53',NULL,'(Mr Kitisuk Piyamitlawan - Director)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
