vers\n\n\n\nKey Benefits:\n⭐ Competitive pricing - 30-40% lower than premium brands\n⭐ Consistent quality - IATF 16949 certified production\n⭐ Flexible ordering - Small MOQ for trial, bulk pricing available\n⭐ Fast turnaround - 30-45 day production lead time\n⭐ Export ready - Professional packaging and documentation\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWe would welcome the opportunity to discuss how 佛山市鼎和盛汽车配件有限公司 can support your business growth. Could we schedule a quick call or video conference at your convenience?\n\nMore information: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nBest regards,\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\n佛山市鼎和盛汽车配件有限公司\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China\n','Reliable Auto Parts Source - Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd | Quality You Can Trust','Dear ร้านขายอะไหล่ยนต์ โคราช เปี๊ยกอะไหล่ยนต์ ปากช่อง Team,\n\nGreetings from Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd! We are a professional automotive exterior parts manufacturer based in Foshan, China.\n\nWe specialize in:\n• Mirror assemblies, pillar trims, roof racks, grilles, fog lamp covers\n\n\nWhy choose us:\n✅ Proven quality with global client base\n✅ Competitive pricing\n✅ Flexible MOQ\n\n\n\n✅ Full export support\n✅ Dedicated customer service\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWe would welcome the opportunity to discuss how we can support your business. Please let us know if you\'d like to receive our product catalog.\n\nVisit us: https://www.carparts-land.com/\n\nLeo Leung\nExport Sales Manager\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd\n? +86 180-7886-5445\n? market@carparts-land.com\n? https://www.carparts-land.com/\n? Foshan City, Guangdong Province, China',60,'C',NULL,1,1,0,NULL,0,'Industry_Directory','thailand_auto_parts_companies.xlsx',NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 19:07:07','2026-06-26 20:17:16',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
